 {title}
 </h1>
 <p class="text-lg text-slate-300">The honest answer most courses won't give you, with real numbers from the Council of Europe and a step by step path that actually works.
 </p>
 <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-6 text-sm text-slate-400">
 <span>April 11, 2026</span>
 <span>•</span>
 <span>9 min read</span>
 </div>
 </div>
